    <lb n="1"/>Αὐρήλιος Δημαρε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὺ</supplied>ς Αὐρηλίᾳ Ἀρσιν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ό</supplied>ῃ τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῇ</supplied> 

    <lb n="2"/>ἀδελφῇ χαίρειν. ἡ προάγουσα παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ πα-

    <lb n="3"/>ρὰ πᾶσι θεοῖς εὐχὴ ἡ περί τε σωτηρί-

    <lb n="4"/>ας σου καὶ τοῦ τέκνου ἡμῶν καὶ τοῦ ἀδελ-

    <lb n="5"/>φοῦ σου καὶ τοῦ πατρό<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς σο</supplied>υ καὶ τῆς μητρός 

    <lb n="6"/>σου καὶ τῶ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> ἡμῶ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> πάντων καὶ πολὺ ἔτι 

    <lb n="7"/>μεῖζον <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῦν</unclear> ἐν τῷ μεγάλῳ Σαραπείῳ 

    <lb n="8"/>π<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ροσκυνεῖ</unclear>, τὸν μέγαν θεὸν Σαρᾶπιν πα-

    <lb n="9"/>ρακαλῶ περί τε τῆς ζωῆς ὑμῶν καὶ τῶν 

    <lb n="10"/>ἡμῶν πάν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied>ων καὶ <subst><add place="inline">τῶν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">χων</del></subst> χρηστῶν ἐλπί-

    <lb n="11"/>δων τῶν ἐν <choice><corr>ἀνθρώποις</corr><sic>ανθρωποισι</sic></choice> <subst><add place="inline">νενομισμέ-

    <lb n="12"/>νων</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">νε<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">σ</del>νομισμενων</del></subst>. τὸ μὲν οὖν γράφειν σοι περὶ 

    <lb n="13"/>τῶν πραγμάτων ἡμῶν ἢ καὶ τῶν ἔργων 

    <lb n="14"/>ὅπερ καὶ φθάνω πολλάκις σοι γράψας 

    <lb n="15"/>διὰ <add place="supralinear"><sic>ε</sic></add> ἐπιστολῶν πολλῶν <add place="supralinear">οὐχ ἧτ<g type="apostrophe"/>τον δὲ</add> καὶ κατ᾽ ὄψιν 

    <lb n="16"/><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">δε</del> σοι ἐνετειλάμην περιτ<g type="apostrophe"/>τὸν νῦν 

    <lb n="17"/>ἡγησάμην, καὶ γὰρ σὺ αὐτὴ μή<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τη</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ</supplied> 

    <lb n="18"/>τυγ<g type="apostrophe"/>χάνουσα τοῦ τέκνου ἡμῶν μᾶ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">λ</supplied>-

    <lb n="19"/>λον ἐμοῦ θελήσεις τὴν τούτων <choice><corr>πρόν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>ι-

    <lb n="20"/>αν</corr><sic>προν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>ινοιαν</sic></choice> καὶ <choice><corr>ἐπανόρθωσιν</corr><sic>επανω<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρθ</supplied>ωσιν</sic></choice> γ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>νέσθαι 

    <lb n="21"/>μετὰ τῆς ἀνυπ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">β</unclear>λήτου κ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">η</supplied>δεμονίας. 

    <lb n="22"/>περὶ δὲ τῆς σεαυτῆς ἐπιμελείας καὶ 

    <lb n="23"/>φροντίδος ἀντὶ παντὸς προνόησον, 

    <lb n="24"/>ὅπερ καὶ περὶ τούτου πολλάκ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>ς σοι ἔγρα-

    <lb n="25"/>ψα, μηδενὸς ὧν ἔχομεν αὐτῶν 

    <lb n="26"/>φειδομένη. ἔπεμψά σοι διὰ Διονυ-

    <lb n="27"/>σίου τοῦ <gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>τος <subst><add place="inline">ἢ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ε</del></subst> ἐν <gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>νομῳ 

    <lb n="28"/>ἢ ἐν τῇ σε<gap reason="lost" extent="6" unit="character"/>α τοῦ γείτονος τῆς 

    <lb n="29"/>οἰκίας τ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῦ Ἀπολλ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ω</unclear>νίου ἐλαίου Σει-

    <lb n="30"/>ρητικοῦ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κοτύλα</supplied>ς ἓξ <num value="6"/> ἐν <choice><corr>ἀγγείῳ</corr><sic>ανγειω</sic></choice> ἡμι-

    <lb n="31"/>χόῳ καὶ τραγη<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μ</supplied>άτων σφυρίδαν 

    <lb n="32"/>μεστὴν μίαν <num value="1"/>. βιβλίδια δύο <num value="2"/> ἐκ Ξει-

    <lb n="33"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear>οφᾶ δοθέντα <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἀπ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ό</unclear> τε Ἀπολλω-

    <lb n="34"/>νίου τοῦ υἱοῦ τοῦ Σκόπα καὶ τοῦ 

    <lb n="35"/><subst><add place="inline">γαμβροῦ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">γαμ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/></del>βρου</del></subst> αὐτοῦ Στεφάνου τοῦ 

    <lb n="36"/>κατὰ <choice><corr>πόλιν</corr><sic>βολιν</sic></choice> κατὰ τοῦ πατρός 

    <lb n="37"/>σου καὶ τῆς μητρός σου καὶ <expan>τούτω<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="38"/>τὰ ἀντίγραφά σοι <expan>διεπεμψάμη<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="39"/>ἐν τῷ ἀπο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δέσ</unclear>μῳ τῶν ἐπιστολῶν· 

    <lb n="40"/>ἐὰν οὖν <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">συ</supplied>ντύχητε καὶ δόξῃ 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="r,ms" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="41" rend="perpendicular"/> τι <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>υμειν</sic></choice> περὶ αὐτῶν, ταχέως μοι δηλώσατε, ὅ τι ἐ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὰ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied> ἐπιδημ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ῶν</unclear> τοῖς

    <lb n="41/42"/><note lang="en" anchored="yes" place="not specified">Writing perpendicular to main text</note> ἐνθάδε 

    <lb n="42" rend="perpendicular"/> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οἷ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>ς ᾤμην ποιεῖν περὶ τούτου μὴ ἀμελησώ περὶ δὲ τοῦ καθ᾽ ἡμᾶς πράγματος 

    <lb n="43" rend="perpendicular"/> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μέ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">χ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρι</unclear> τούτου <choice><corr>οὐδὲν</corr><sic>οδυδεν</sic></choice> ἐγένετο. ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι <gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="44" rend="perpendicular"/> <gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αρ</unclear>ιο<gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/>ς δια<gap reason="lost" extent="14" unit="character"/> 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="45"/>μηδέν μοι ἐν τῷ παρόντι <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">δι</del> ἐπιμηνιδίων <choice><corr>διαπέμψησθε</corr><sic>διαππεμψησθαι</sic></choice> ἔστ᾽ ἂν <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>υμειν</sic></choice> πε-

    <lb n="46"/>ρὶ τούτου δηλώσω ἢ καὶ γράψω. τοὺς ἡμῶν πάντας κατ᾽ ὄνομα προσ-

    <lb n="47"/>αγόρευε καί <choice><corr>ἄσπασαι</corr><sic>ασπασε</sic></choice>. πάνυ δ᾽ <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>υμειν</sic></choice> εὐχαριστῶ ὅτι πολλάκις ἐμοῦ γρά-

    <lb n="48"/>ψαντος <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>υμειν</sic></choice> ὑμεῖς οὐδὲ ὅλως ἐγράψατε οὐδὲ ἐμνήσθητέ μου περὶ τῆς 

    <lb n="49"/>ἀσφαλείας τῆς οἰκίας ἡμῶν, ὡς καὶ πολλάκις διὰ γραμμάτων καὶ ἐπιστο-

    <lb n="50"/>λῶν καὶ κατ᾽ ὄψιν παρὼν <choice><corr>ἐνετειλάμην</corr><sic>ενετιλαμην</sic></choice>. μὴ ἀμελήσῃς μὴ ἄρα ποτὲ θέ-

    <lb n="51"/>λῃς <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>τὰ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>ῦ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Ἡρ</supplied>α<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear>ί<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δι</unclear> τὴν τήρησιν τῆς ὅλης οἰκίας παραδιδόναι ἀ-

    <lb n="52"/>χρήστο<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">υ</unclear> οὔσης αὐτῆς καί, ὃ μὴ εἴη, <choice><corr>ἀλ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">λ᾽</supplied></corr><sic>αλ</sic></choice> ἐξ ἄλλω<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ν</unclear> γένηται. τοῦ παιδα-

    <lb n="53"/>ρίου Πτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>λεμαίου τοῦ ἀδελφοῦ Ἑρμογένους ἐξερχομένου εἰς τὴν Ἀλεξάν-

    <lb n="54"/>δρειαν πολλάκις ἐλθόντος πρὸς <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἐμ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὲ οὐ τεθελήκατε α</supplied>ὐτῷ διδόναι ἐπιστο-

    <lb n="55"/>λὰς οὐδ᾽ ὅλως <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὐτὸν</supplied> προσήκατε, ἀλλὰ καὶ Εὐδ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αίμων</supplied> αὐτῷ ἀπετάξατο 

    <lb n="56"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">λ</supplied>έγων ὅτι ἐν τῷ παρόντι οὐ σχολάζομεν ἑτέροις ἐξερχόμενοι. 

    <lb n="57"/><expan>ἀπόδ<ex cert="high">ος</ex></expan> Ἀρσινόῃ ἀδελφῇ <expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> Δημάρεως. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.31317" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31317" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="201" notAfter="300">III</date></p></div><div n="meta.31317" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.31317" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">7</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1070</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">31317</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">7</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1070</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;7;1070" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31317" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">241</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.31317" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31317" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Tibiletti, Lettere private 16</bibl></div><div n="meta.31317" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org